Class RocksTimeQueue<T>

java.lang.Object
dev.rocksqueue.core.RocksTimeQueue<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
TimeQueue<T>, AutoCloseable
public class RocksTimeQueue<T> extends Object implements TimeQueue<T>
RocksDB-backed time-based FIFO queue with binary-encoded keys. Per-queue-group instance (separate RocksDB per group).
